  "text": "This new record of G. turbidus increases the number of snake species in Hidalgo state to 84 [CITATION_1] . With the new record of this species from Hidalgo, the importance and necessity for conservation of the pine and cloud forests where G. turbidus and other species of amphibians and reptiles live is highlighted.",
